  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153600/extras/85819596ded8b9416c13e6c32bd99e76.avif?t=1682627256\" width=640 height=132 /></span><br>Hero Jumper is a sandbox first-person shooter game, where you can break every single object to its smallest parts. Destroy enemies that try to kill you on the wild map. Or download maps from the workshop.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153600/extras/e214762a6a8d20557b88a492f05ac6ab.poster.avif?t=1682627256\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153600/extras/e214762a6a8d20557b88a492f05ac6ab.webm?t=1682627256\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153600/extras/e214762a6a8d20557b88a492f05ac6ab.mp4?t=1682627256\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"> <li>Procedural Destruction<br> </li><li>First Person Shooter<br> </li><li>Level Editor (Scripting Support)<br> </li><li>Workshop Downloading/Uploading</li></ul>",
